 on-chip, with 1.65(1) dB\ndirectly measured, which is the largest amount of squeezing yet reported from\nany nanophotonic source.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 26 Jan 2020 15:52:18 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 8 Nov 2020 18:15:33 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-04-28"}
